TableContextTimeStampBeforeTable: {738=Chances are there's a PetSmart store right around the corner! PetSmart has over 1,300 locations across the United States and Canada, including New Mexico. Many of our stores offer world-class pet services and facilities. We stock everything from the essential supplies for all pets, like food, feeding accessories, treats, toys and bedding to the latest in health and wellness. Our New Mexico locations have the solutions you need for the lifetime needs of your pet, including a wide selection for small specialty pets: habitats, aquariums, and naturalistic decor. Did you know? Through its in-store pet adoption partnership with PetSmart Charities, PetSmart has helped save the lives of more than 5 million pets since 1994.}
